data.description: Wonderful home on large corner lot features an open floor plan with hardwood floors through out the main level, great room with fireplace, gorgeous kitchen with island that offers bar seating, stainless steal appliances, granite counter tops, tile back splash, pantry and recessed lighting. On the upper level you'll find a large master bedroom with walk in closet and master bathroom with double vanities, garden tub and separate shower, two additional bedrooms with a shared bathroom, a 8x11 loft and laundry room. There is a nice patio area out back, the yard is nicely landscaped with irrigation system, and there is a double car garage. Great location just outside of Fort Gordon gate 2 and close to plenty of Shopping and Restaurants. You wont want to miss this one!!
